getPSDELogicNodes.name: 计算我的
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select ((case when ? is null then 0 else ? end )+ (case when ? is null then 0 else ? end ) + (case when ? is null then 0 else ? end ) + (case when ? is null then 0 else ? end )) as MYTERRITORYCNT from dual

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 项目数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql:
SELECT
	count( t1.id ) as PROJECTS
FROM
	zt_project t1 
WHERE
	t1.deleted = '0' 
	AND (
	t1.acl = 'open' 
	OR t1.OPENEDBY = ? 
	OR t1.pm = ? 
	OR t1.PO = ? 
	OR t1.RD =?	OR t1.QD = ?
	OR (
	t1.acl = 'private' 
	AND t1.id IN ( SELECT t3.root FROM zt_team t3 WHERE t3.account = ? AND t3.type = 'project' ) 
	) 
	)

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 计算我的收藏数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select ((case when ? is null then 0 else ? end )+ (case when ? is null then 0 else ? end ) + (case when ? is null then 0 else ? end )) as MYFAVORITES from dual

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 产品数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql:
SELECT
		count( t1.id ) AS PRODUCTS 
	FROM
		zt_product t1 
	WHERE
		t1.deleted = '0' 
		AND (
			t1.acl = 'open' 
			OR t1.CREATEDBY =?
			OR t1.PO = ?
			OR t1.RD = ? 
			OR t1.QD = ? 
			OR t1.id IN (
			SELECT
				t.product 
			FROM
				zt_projectproduct t 
			WHERE
				t.project IN ( SELECT t3.root FROM zt_team t3 WHERE t3.account = ? AND t3.type = 'project' ) 
			) 
	)

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 我的收藏Bug数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t1.id) AS MYFAVORITEBUGS from zt_bug t1 where t1.deleted = '0' and t1.id in (select t.OBJECTID from T_IBZ_FAVORITES t where t.type = 'bug' and t.account = ?)

getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t1.id) AS MYFAVORITESTORYS from zt_story t1 where t1.deleted = '0' and t1.id in (select t.OBJECTID from T_IBZ_FAVORITES t where t.type = 'story' and t.account = ?)

getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t1.id) AS MYFAVORITETASKS from zt_task t1 where t1.deleted = '0' and t1.id in (select t.OBJECTID from T_IBZ_FAVORITES t where t.type = 'task' and t.account = ?)
